Royal Ossuary Apex~
@@yWind-scored@@N sandstone banner poles sag beneath veils of @@bblue@@N shadow, where chiselled dynastic faces are worn smooth by centuries of desert abrasion. Shards of enamel and brass peek from drifts, suggesting this district was once extravagant before the sun consumed it.


A lane of broken markers forks and rejoins in confusing angles around fallen lintels. faint chimes tremble under the sun, and every gust carries the dry taste of old tomb air from somewhere deeper in the city.


No scavengers linger here; the chamber is held as a lethal dueling ground, untouched by lesser wanderers.~
